Third-party notices

This project is a design-reference gallery. Some demos deliberately reproduce
or take inspiration from third-party designs for educational purposes:

  * Several demos emulate the look of well-known products (e.g. Stripe, Vercel,
    Linear, Apple, Airbnb, Cyworld). All product names, logos, and brands are
    trademarks of their respective owners. The MIT license above covers only
    the original code in this repository, not those trademarks or brand
    identities.

  * demos/card-tilt-3d.html reproduces the holographic-foil / spring showcase
    technique from simey's "pokemon-cards-css" project. The in-file attribution
    to the original author is retained and must be preserved.

  * Miniature 3D ride images and the parchment map in assets/gen/ were produced
    with an AI image generator (Higgsfield) for use within this project.

If you reuse this code, keep this notice and the per-file attributions intact.
